title: march 8: flight MH370 (with Sigrid)
description:
In this episode of 365 days with mxmtoon, Maia talks about the disappearance of Malaysia Airlines Flight MH370 and the ensuing mystery about what happened to it. She also hears from an amazing musical guest, Sigrid! Listen to this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
